reviewText: Couldn't go through with course.  Sounded like I was getting taught by an 8 year old.  I'll keep it at that so as not to come across as a... you know what.  Hope review helps.
Good and the best course in Corona time

I think the instructor could have put in a bit more effort and instead of the reading practices, showed us the same examples via more video tutorials. There were many new and unknown terminologies and concepts in the reading practices so it would have been better had the instructor explained them and solved the problems via video tutorials.

In my opinion the course focuses too much at Tableau. I would have expected to be more focused on Generate Insights with using Tableau for examples, while for me the case is exactly the opposite - Tableau tutorial using Statistics as example data.
the instructor needs to have less robotic tone and be more interactive but other than that the course is great
